## `v8.writeHeapSnapshot([filename[,options]])`

<!-- YAML
added: v11.13.0
changes:
  - version: v19.1.0
    pr-url: https://github.com/nodejs/node/pull/44989
    description: Support options to configure the heap snapshot.
  - version: v18.0.0
